Label: Time
Description: Abstract measure covering the concept of time

Label: Instant
Description: A particular point in time

Label: Count
Description: A count of events or things

Label: Index
Description: An index calculation of of a base

Label: Elapsed Time

Label: Reponse Time

Label: Wait Time

Label: Hold Time

Description: A count of flights

Label: Count of people

Description: A count of passengers

Label: Number of Visits to Port

Label: Number of Unique Ship
Description: A count of unique ships

Label: Count of Companies
Description: A count of companies

Label: Amount of Money

Label: Gross Weekly Pay
Description: Gross weekly pay

Label: People in Employment
Description: People who are in paid or who are employeed but on temporary leave

Label: Area
Description: Area

Description: The size of an area of land
